name: Xoco - Head
description:
An ancient mask covers her head, Xoco will pull it over her face in dangerous situations to protect and spread fear.

She lives as a renowned warrior, feared by some but respected by all. She finally achieved her dreams of greatness, albeit not in the way she had initially imagined.

This NFT is part of the Contaverse gaming universe, learn more here: https://contaquest.com
